# EconoSuite

A CLI for preparing economics manuscripts of submission-ready quality in `.docx` format.
Integrating data from R/Python regressions and enforcing strict journal structures (e.g. AER).

## Installation

```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Usage

```bash
econosuite init
econosuite check
econosuite build
```
